---
import AdminLayout from '../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
import { env } from '../../lib/env';

const ical = env.PUBLIC_SITE_URL;
---
<AdminLayout title="Definições">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <section class="rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="font-medium mb-3">Email transaccional</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Configure <code class="px-1 bg-stone-100 rounded">RESEND_API_KEY</code> e <code class="px-1 bg-stone-100 rounded">EMAIL_FROM</code> no Railway. Em modo de desenvolvimento, os emails são impressos no terminal.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-2">Estado: <strong>{import.meta.env.RESEND_API_KEY ? 'configurado' : 'apenas console (dev)'}</strong></p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="font-medium mb-3">Inteligência de preços (IA)</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Modelo: <code class="px-1 bg-stone-100 rounded">{import.meta.env.ANTHROPIC_MODEL ?? 'claude-haiku-4-5-20251001'}</code></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-2">Orçamento mensal: {import.meta.env.AI_PRICING_MONTHLY_BUDGET_EUR ?? '5'} EUR</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">Estado: <strong>{import.meta.env.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY ? 'activo' : 'sem chave'}</strong></p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 lg:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="font-medium mb-3">Cron jobs</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-3">Pode chamar estes endpoints a partir de qualquer scheduler (Railway Cron, GitHub Actions, etc.) com o header <code class="px-1 bg-stone-100 rounded">Authorization: Bearer $CRON_SECRET</code>.</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-mono text-stone-700">
        <li>POST <a class="underline" href="/api/cron/scrape-competitors">{ical}/api/cron/scrape-competitors</a></li>
        <li>POST <a class="underline" href="/api/cron/suggest-prices">{ical}/api/cron/suggest-prices?days=45</a></li>
        <li>POST <a class="underline" href="/api/cron/ical-import">{ical}/api/cron/ical-import</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 lg:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="font-medium mb-3">Variáveis de ambiente</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Edite via <code class="px-1 bg-stone-100 rounded">railway variables --set CHAVE=valor</code> ou no painel da Railway. Após alterar, faça redeploy.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</AdminLayout>
